  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to telepathy-farstream</title>

    <para>
      The <application>telepathy-farstream</application> is a Telepathy 
      client library that uses Farstream to handle Call channels.
    </para>

    &lfs70_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
      <listitem>
